<cb:div>
<pb n="0009a" xml:id="I01.0004.0009a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0009a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 4</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0009a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>韓貞等造石窟記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0009a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0009a0101">員外散騎常侍昌黎韓貞。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a02" type="honorific"/><note n="0009001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">葥＝前【史】</note><note n="0009001" resp="ihp" type="mod">葥【佛拓】，前【史】</note><app n="0009001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】">葥</rdg></app>建德郡<note n="0009002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">承＝丞【史】</note><note n="0009002" resp="ihp" type="mod">承【佛拓】，丞【史】</note><app n="0009002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">承</rdg></app>沃連戍軍主呂安辰。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a03" type="honorific"/>夫至道無名。故顯名以為真。玄<note n="0009003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥥒＝寂【史】</note><note n="0009003" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥥒【佛拓】，寂【史】</note><app n="0009003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥥒</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0009a04" type="honorific"/>難辯。假<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">幻</unclear>象以明壞。是以如來□道
<lb ed="I" n="0009a05" type="honorific"/>以濟萬類。大推隨方而拔群溺。□□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a06" type="honorific"/>更<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">陶</unclear>□造。品物<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">咸</unclear>享者也。斯寔□□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a07" type="honorific"/>之典。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">御</unclear>九聖之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">師</unclear>光。自<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">非</unclear>刊石荊山。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a08" type="honorific"/>真容將來□蠹□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">嗟</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恤</unclear>於是与
<lb ed="I" n="0009a09" type="honorific"/>沃<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">黎</unclear>戍軍主呂安辰。隊主劉都〃。劉
<lb ed="I" n="0009a10" type="honorific"/>初丹。張惠初。劉胡堤等七十四人。□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a11" type="honorific"/>趣<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">府</unclear><note n="0009004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㝵＝碍【史】</note><note n="0009004" resp="ihp" type="mod">㝵【佛拓】，碍【史】</note><app n="0009004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">碍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㝵</rdg></app>三途。覬一豪之善。有所因感
<lb ed="I" n="0009a12" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">於</unclear>夷方之右。沃黎之西。建造私窟。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a13" type="honorific"/>是以暉聖容且表微塵之心耳。□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a14" type="honorific"/>來因果。上鐘景明。下及蜫虫<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">不</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a15" type="honorific"/>無二。聊記年月也。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a16" type="honorific"/>玄樞至妙。太虛檄文。檄陳□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">範</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0009a17" type="honorific"/>悟<note n="0009005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣴴＝海【史】</note><note n="0009005" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣴴【佛拓】，海【史】</note><app n="0009005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣴴</rdg></app>淪滅<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">空</unclear>明<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">定</unclear>象法敷□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a18" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">濟</unclear>□生集為珍
<lb ed="I" n="0009a19" type="honorific"/>大魏景明三年五月九日造。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a20" type="honorific"/>尉劉□丹使員外散騎常侍昌黎韓貞。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a21" type="honorific"/>前建德郡<app type="star" corresp="#0009002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">承</rdg></app>沃<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">黎</unclear>戍軍主呂安辰。
<lb ed="I" n="0009a22" type="honorific"/>尉喻使令史□國淳于敬□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0009a23" type="honorific"/>　　隊主劉都〃
<lb ed="I" n="0009a24" type="honorific"/>　　隊主張惠初
<lb ed="I" n="0009a25" type="honorific"/>　　隊主劉初丹
<lb ed="I" n="0009a26" type="honorific"/>　　賢者劉護堤</p>
